WEBVTT

00:07:30.958 --> 00:07:33.286
Lakini sijawahi kujihisi na sikuwa mfungwa.

00:07:36.236 --> 00:07:38.561
Kitu cha msingi nilichojifunza

00:07:38.585 --> 00:07:40.863
ni kwamba kama ningewaza,

00:07:40.887 --> 00:07:43.069
na kama unawaza, unaweza,

00:07:43.093 --> 00:07:44.243
utaweza.

00:07:44.601 --> 00:07:47.346
Lakini kama unakaa unawaza hauwezi,

00:07:47.370 --> 00:07:48.520
hautaweza.

00:07:49.593 --> 00:07:51.126
Ni rahisi kama hivyo.

00:07:52.259 --> 00:07:54.760
Na ninapata tumaini kutokana na mapinduzi ya amani

00:07:54.784 --> 00:07:56.060
niliyosikia katika hatua hii.

00:07:56.633 --> 00:07:59.434
Dunia inakuhitaji sasa, dunia inakuhitaji leo.